content: Gemini 3 is powering the next generation of reliable, production-ready AI agents. This post highlights 6 open-source framework collaborations (ADK, Agno, Browser Use, Eigent, Letta, mem0), demonstrating practical agentic workflows for tasks like deep search, multi-agent systems, browser and enterprise automation, and stateful agents with advanced memory. Clone the examples and start building today.
